title: Quickly, Reset!
description:
Description :
        *It's been several years since we met at work and became close, and the guy I've been secretly (really?) in love with says he gets sick every two weeks. His weird way of drawing lines is really annoying, so this time I went over there without hesitation...What is that thing on your head and that thing on your bu**?Even asking for help with something like that~?!*
